Citation.sTitle: Determination and Correlation of the Solubility of l-Fucose in Four Binary Solvent Systems at the Temperature Range from 288.15 to 308.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: Experimental solubility data of -fucose in methanol + water, ethanol + water, 2-propanol + water and acetone + water systems were measured at temperatures ranging from 288.15 K to 308.15 K under atmosphere pressure (P = 0.1 MPa), using the gravimetric method.
